    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>How Satan Gains Entrance to the Soul</strong>&mdash;All should guard the senses, lest Satan gain victory over them; for these are the avenues of the soul.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">2<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"3T 507.1\" data-link=\"119.2389\">Testimonies for the Church 3:507</span>.</span></a></sup>",
