    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "You will have to become a faithful sentinel over your eyes, ears, and all your senses if you would control your mind and prevent vain and corrupt thoughts from staining your soul. The power of grace alone can accomplish this most desirable work.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"2T 561.1\" data-link=\"120.2407\">Testimonies for the Church 2:561</span>.</span></a></sup>",
