    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Satan and his angels are busy creating a paralyzed condition of the senses so that cautions, warnings, and reproofs shall not be heard; or, if heard, that they shall not take effect upon the heart and reform the life.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"5T 493.1\" data-link=\"113.2422\">Ibid., 5:493</span>.</span></a></sup>",
