    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Satan Cannot Enter the Mind Without Our Consent</strong>&mdash;We should present before the people the fact that God has provided that we shall not be tempted above what we are able to bear, but that with every temptation He will make a way of escape. If we live wholly for God, we shall not allow the mind to indulge in selfish imaginings.",
