    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Close Every Avenue to the Tempter</strong>&mdash;All who name the name of Christ need to watch and pray and guard the avenues of the soul, for Satan is at work to corrupt and destroy if the least advantage is given him.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"3T 476.1\" data-link=\"119.2236\">Testimonies for the Church 3:476</span>.</span></a></sup>",
